headline: Cincinnati Financial Corporation Declares Regular Quarterly Cash Dividend
summary: Cincinnati Financial Corporation (Nasdaq: CINF) announced that at today's regular meeting, the board of directors declared an 81-cents-per-share regular quarterly cash dividend. The dividend is payable January 15, 2025, to shareholders of record as of December 19, 2024.

headline: Cincinnati Financial Corporation Announces Changes to Board of Directors
summary: Cincinnati Financial Corporation (Nasdaq: CINF) today announced that Thomas J. Aaron has resigned from the board of directors of Cincinnati Financial Corporation and boards of affiliated companies. At the same time, the board reduced its size to 13 members. Mr. Aaron's resignation is not the result of a disagreement with any of the companies on any matter relating to their operations, policies or practices.
